OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1773885783
OL,3,CCovid-19 pandemic probe to set out
OL,4,Cimpact on NHS and patients
OL,6,FThe harrowing impact of the
OL,7,Fcoronavirus pandemic on patients and
OL,8,FNHS staff is to be laid bare in a new
OL,9,Freport.
OL,11,FThe UK Covid-19 Public Inquiry is set
OL,12,Fto publish insights on how the
OL,13,Fhealthcare system in Britain coped in
OL,14,Fthe face of the virus.
OL,16,FA number of health leaders broke down
OL,17,Fas they gave powerful testimony to the
OL,18,Fpandemic probe in 2024.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1773885783
OL,3,CCovid-19 pandemic probe to set out
OL,4,Cimpact on NHS and patients
OL,6,FThey included a senior medic who broke
OL,7,Fdown in tears as he described scenes
OL,8,F"from hell" on intensive care wards,
OL,9,Fwith staff running out of body bags
OL,10,Fand sick patients "raining from the
OL,11,Fsky".
OL,13,FProfessor Kevin Fong ` former national
OL,14,Fclinical adviser in emergency
OL,15,Fpreparedness, resilience and response
OL,16,Fat NHS England ` told the probe that
OL,17,Fthe scale of death on intensive care
OL,18,Funits was "truly astounding" and how
OL,19,Fone hospital he visited was close to
OL,20,Fcollapse.
OL,26,@pD@AOUpD@KO]rD@SOUsD@DO]zD@KOUzD@\O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1773885783
OL,3,CCovid-19 pandemic probe to set out
OL,4,Cimpact on NHS and patients
OL,6,FFormer chief nursing officer for
OL,7,FEngland Dame Ruth May described how
OL,8,Fthe NHS in England went into the
OL,9,Fpandemic with 40,000 fewer nurses than
OL,10,Fit needed.
OL,12,FThe inquiry heard that in critical
OL,13,Fcare, highly skilled nurses usually
OL,14,Fcare for patients on a one-to-one
OL,15,Fbasis, but during the crisis a
OL,16,Fdecision was made to increase the
OL,17,Fnumber of patients cared for by each
OL,18,Fnurse as patient numbers swelled, with
OL,19,Fnurses in these units caring for as
OL,20,Fmany as six patients at once.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
