CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1773885783
OL,3,CCovid-19 pandemic probe to set out
OL,4,Cimpact on NHS and patients
OL,6,FElsewhere former health secretary Matt
OL,7,FHancock told the inquiry that
OL,8,FEngland's hospitals were within
OL,9,F"hours" of running out of some items
OL,10,Fof personal protective equipment (PPE)
OL,11,Fin the early months of the pandemic.
OL,13,FMr Hancock also said he "reluctantly"
OL,14,Fapproved of the decision to pause non-
OL,15,Furgent planned care during the
OL,16,Fpandemic.
OL,18,FThe Government prioritised hospital
OL,19,Fcapacity for Covid-19 and emergency
OL,20,Fpatients, and so paused elective (non-
OL,21,Furgent) treatment in spring 2020.
OL,26,@qD@AOUqD@GO]uD@YOUuD@eO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1773885783
OL,3,CCovid-19 pandemic probe to set out
OL,4,Cimpact on NHS and patients
OL,6,FThis led to growing waiting lists and
OL,7,Fmeant thousands of people who needed
OL,8,Fcare for non-Covid reasons had to wait
OL,9,For could not access treatment.
OL,11,FThe former MP also defended the Stay
OL,12,FHome, Save Lives, Protect the NHS
OL,13,Fmessaging implemented during the
OL,14,Fpandemic.
OL,16,FBut England's chief medical officer,
OL,17,FProfessor Sir Chris Whitty, said
OL,18,Fofficials "didn't get it across well
OL,19,Fenough" that people should continue to
OL,20,Fgo to hospital for serious illnesses
OL,21,Fother than Covid.
OL,26,@zD@KOU{D@GO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
