PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1773885783
OL,3,CCovid-19 pandemic probe to set out
OL,4,Cimpact on NHS and patients
OL,6,FHowever, he said the UK faced an
OL,7,F"absolutely catastrophic situation" as
OL,8,Fit headed towards the first Covid
OL,9,Flockdown and, without such a measure,
OL,10,Fthere were very serious concerns about
OL,11,Fhow the NHS would cope.
OL,13,FCritics of lockdowns have pointed to
OL,14,Fthe numbers of people who died from
OL,15,Fnon-Covid conditions which may have
OL,16,Fbeen treatable, but where the person
OL,17,Fstayed at home or could not access
OL,18,Fnormal NHS care.
OL,26,@oD@AOUoD@cO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1773885783
OL,3,CCovid-19 pandemic probe to set out
OL,4,Cimpact on NHS and patients
OL,6,FInquiry chairwoman Baroness Heather
OL,7,FHallett examined all aspects of the
OL,8,FNHS during the crisis.
OL,10,FThis included how managers led the
OL,11,Fpandemic response, the role of primary
OL,12,Fcare and GPs, NHS backlogs and how the
OL,13,Fvaccine programme was integrated.
OL,15,FThe diagnosis of long Covid and the
OL,16,Fsupport offered to those affected was
OL,17,Falso analysed as part of the inquiry's
OL,18,FModule 3, which will report its
OL,19,Ffindings on Thursday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1773885783
OL,3,CCovid-19 pandemic probe to set out
OL,4,Cimpact on NHS and patients
OL,6,FIn a statement, Covid-19 Bereaved
OL,7,FFamilies for Justice said: "The Module
OL,8,F3 report must not pull its punches.
OL,10,F"Years of austerity left the NHS
OL,11,Fdangerously exposed before Covid ever
OL,12,Farrived, without the capacity,
OL,13,Fresilience or headroom needed to cope
OL,14,Fwith a major shock.
OL,16,F"Many of our loved ones died in
OL,17,Fhorrific conditions because ministers
OL,18,Ffailed to strengthen the health
OL,19,Fservice when they had the chance.
OL,26,@oD@\OUrD@AOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30409
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1773885783
OL,3,CCovid-19 pandemic probe to set out
OL,4,Cimpact on NHS and patients
OL,6,F"The inquiry must not indulge the
OL,7,Ffalse claim pushed by Boris Johnson
OL,8,Fand Matt Hancock that the NHS coped
OL,9,Fwith Covid.
OL,11,F"It did not.
OL,13,F"Hospitals were overwhelmed, staff
OL,14,Fwere stretched beyond breaking point,
OL,15,Fand patients paid the price.
OL,17,F"The report must make clear that
OL,18,Frestoring funding and capacity is now
OL,19,Fa matter of national urgency.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUuD@AOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30410
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1773885783
OL,3,CCovid-19 pandemic probe to set out
OL,4,Cimpact on NHS and patients
OL,6,F"We are less prepared now than we were
OL,7,Fin 2020, and unless that changes, more
OL,8,Flives will be put at risk when the
OL,9,Fnext crisis comes."
OL,11,FIt comes as the Government announced
OL,12,Fplans to give people stronger rights
OL,13,Ffor hospital and care home visits.
OL,15,FConcerns were raised over visitation
OL,16,Frights after visits were curtailed
OL,17,Fduring the pandemic amid efforts to
OL,18,Fstop the spread of Covid-19.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@SO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30411
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1773885783
OL,3,CCovid-19 pandemic probe to set out
OL,4,Cimpact on NHS and patients
OL,6,FChanges in the law were initially
OL,7,Fproposed in 2023 by the former
OL,8,FConservative government.
OL,10,FNow the new Government has said that
OL,11,Fit will "distribute comprehensive
OL,12,Fguidance and resources to make
OL,13,Fvisitation rights clear".
OL,15,FThe Department of Health and Social
OL,16,FCare said that ministers are
OL,17,F"exploring bringing forward proposals
OL,18,Ffor legislating visiting rights as
OL,19,Fpart of wider reform work".
OL,26,@sD@IOUuD@XO]yD@AOU{D@ZO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30412
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1773885783
OL,3,CCovid-19 pandemic probe to set out
OL,4,Cimpact on NHS and patients
OL,6,FThe guidance will make clear that
OL,7,Fpatients and residents in care homes,
OL,8,Fhospitals and hospices "will no longer
OL,9,Fbe cut off from their loved ones
OL,10,Funless in exceptional circumstances",
OL,11,Fthe department said.
OL,13,FCare minister Stephen Kinnock said:
OL,14,F"No one should be separated from their
OL,15,Floved ones unnecessarily. Contact with
OL,16,Ffamily and friends should not be seen
OL,17,Fas a luxury but a basic part of good
OL,18,Fcare.
OL,26,@pD@XOUrD@dO]vD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30413
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1773885783
OL,3,CCovid-19 pandemic probe to set out
OL,4,Cimpact on NHS and patients
OL,6,F"These changes will protect patients
OL,7,Fand residents, give families a
OL,8,Fstronger voice, and help make sure
OL,9,Fcare is more compassionate, open and
OL,10,Fhumane."
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@HO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/13
